title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1987-09-16
description:
Set I
Touch of Grey >
Scarlet Begonias
Little Red Rooster
Dire Wolf
My Brother Esau
High Time
Let it Grow >
Don't Ease Me In
Set II
Bertha >
Greatest Story Ever Told >
Devil With the Blue Dress On >
Good Golly Miss Molly >
Devil With the Blue Dress On (reprise) >
He's Gone >
Drums >
Space >
Truckin' >
Wharf Rat >
Throwing Stones >
Not Fade Away

Encore:
Not Fade Away (reprise) >
Goin' Down the Road Feeling Bad (coda) >
Black Muddy River
 
Comment
New York City Percussion Ensemble Opened

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
